This magic shield offers a degree of control over the seas. While attuned to this shield, gain [[advantage]] when operating a water-based vehicle. In addition, you can cast the [[control water]] spell. Gain [[advantage]] when you use this spell to attempt to magically change the direction of a water-based vehicle within 300 feet of you that has a rudder; you may even be able to wrest control of the vehicle away from a creature who is currently controlling its rudder.